  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nGSN is moving from v1 to v2. Current GSN support in contracts is based around v1, which is being deprecated of the more modular approach that is GSN v2.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nSupport for ERC2771 is the topic of another issue & PR. In order to cleanup the repo, and avoid possible confusion between the old and new GSN tolling, the `contracts/GSN` repository should be removed.\r\n\r\nAny comments is welcome.",
